data.description:
METICULOUSLY CARED FOR BY ORIGINAL OWNER! TURN KEY ~ EXPANSIVE CORNER LOT, HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER PRIMROSE MODEL! GORGEOUS MOUNTAIN VIEWS FROM BRIGHT & AIRY KITCHEN W/NOOK AREA. PRIMARY BEDROOM W/BACKYARD VIEWS SEPERATE FROM GUEST ROOMS. PRIMARY BATH HOSTS A NEW CUSTOM WALK IN TUB/SHOWER FOR COMFORT, SAFETY & PAMPERING, WALK IN CLOSET. CEILING FANS IN ALL BEDROOMS/LIVING ROOM. NEWER A/C UNIT, HOT WATER HEATER, DISHWASHER & TRASH COMPACTOR. HOME CONVEYS WITH W/WATER SOFTENER & TESLA SOLAR LEASE. COVERED PATIO FACING SOUTH FOR BEAUTIFUL VIEWS. HOME BOASTS PLANTATION SHUTTERS THROUGHOUT W/CUSTOM PANELS & DECORATIVE HARDWARE ADORNING ALL WINDOWS & SLIDER TO PATIO. 
THIS IS THE PERFECT ~ MOVE-IN READY SUN CITY ALIANTE HOME FOR YOU!!! AMENITIES GALORE FOR ALL RESIDENTS INCLUDING FITNESS CENTER, TENNIS, PICKLEBALL, POOL, COMMUNITY CENTER W/EVENTS & CLUBS, PUBLIC GOLF COURSE, VETERAN ACTIVITIES! ONLY 14 MILES FROM THE LAS VEGAS STRIP & MINUTES FROM YOUR VERY OWN NEIGHBORHOOD ALIANTE CASINO.
